Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.47,0:00:02.69,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}As bright as a spark,\Nwith a sharp and precise wit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.69,0:00:04.46,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Once he gets started,\Nyou can't stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.46,0:00:06.61,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Summer vacation's only just begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.61,0:00:08.65,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What kind of guy has\NSonoko taken a liking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.65,0:00:10.40,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth\Nfor what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.40,0:00:12.78,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid\Nbut has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.78,0:00:15.03,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name?\NDetective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.11,0:01:40.91,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}At the beach in Izu, Ran and I\Nwitnessed a strange summer event!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.91,0:01:45.16,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Somehow, Sonoko got herself a boyfriend by the name of Michiwaki{\rHonorifics - Narration Off\be10}-san{\r\be10}!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.58,0:01:48.75,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But while Sonoko's\Nin seventh heaven,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.75,0:01:52.30,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}waiting for Michiwaki{\rHonorifics - Narration Off\be10}-san{\r\be10} to\Npick her up for their dinner date,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.30,0:01:54.63,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}someone attacked her!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.43,0:02:03.77,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Am I imagining things,\Nor does this guy keep watching us?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:09.02,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Then there's that guy in the glasses who Ran thinks she's seen somewhere before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.23,0:02:12.94,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And as for the guy\Nwho attacked Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.86,0:02:18.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Was he really just a simple thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.93,0:02:39.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:45.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a lovely restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:47.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There don't seem to be\Nmany customers, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.52,0:02:50.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe we came too early.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.02,0:02:55.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you\Naren't coming, Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.86,0:02:57.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.24,0:03:00.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because I kept remembering that guy last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:03.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't sleep much,\Nso I'm going to sleep here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:07.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, all right.\NBut what a waste...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.96,0:03:12.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, there are drinks in this cooler,\Nso help yourself whenever you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:15.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:18.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, we'll see you later, Sonoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.05,0:03:19.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have a nice time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:27.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, if you're feeling up to it\Nafter your nap, join us in the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.47,0:03:29.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:36.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't stay up another minute...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.78,0:03:42.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The seafood here is delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.99,0:03:46.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a shame, since I wanted to let Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} try it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:50.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You think she'll be all right?\NShe's sleeping inside a hot car.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:53.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I turned\Nthe air conditioner on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:04:01.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, look at this!\NIs this for one person?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.97,0:04:02.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:04.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's plenty\Nand the price is low.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:06.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the secret to\Nthis restaurant's popularity!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:10.56,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh geez. A full-course\Nmeal for lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:28.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See? Didn't I tell you\Nthe food was great?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.74,0:04:30.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, it was delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:32.87,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm completely stuffed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.41,0:04:35.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.08,0:04:37.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I feel a bit bad\Nfor Sonoko though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:38.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.79,0:04:40.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're from the inn...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:44.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you come here often?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:45.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, this is my first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:49.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, where's your\Nbrown-haired friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:51.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen her anywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:53.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:54.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems she's\Na bit sleep-deprived,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:57.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so she's resting in\Nthe car parked outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.94,0:04:58.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:01.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that your car, Michiwaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:04.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Why's it moving?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.03,0:05:06.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is bad! It's heading\Nstraight for the cliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:15.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please come again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.79,0:05:21.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, where do you think\Nyou're going? Pay your bill!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.55,0:05:30.85,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's a lockpick!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:38.77,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The hand brake's disengaged!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:40.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko, wake up! Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:45.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I can't put full strength in\Nwhile I'm running!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.36,0:05:49.32,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh no!\NWe're almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.32,0:05:51.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r},\Nget away from the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.96,0:06:05.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:10.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko, grab onto me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.90,0:06:28.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!\NAre you guys all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:30.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah... Somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.03,0:06:35.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was close.\NI'm glad you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.29,0:06:36.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:38.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you put\Nthe hand brake on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.25,0:06:41.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous!\NI {\i1}did{\i0} have it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:45.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it weren't on, the car would've\Nfallen off the cliff a lot sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.30,0:06:48.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone released the hand brake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.68,0:06:54.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone broke into the car\Nusing a lockpick.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:58.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone who was after\NSonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}'s life.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.69,0:07:04.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.78,0:07:10.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So someone broke into the car\Nwhile Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was asleep inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.99,0:07:13.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,released the hand brake,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.82,0:07:19.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and made the car roll down\Nthis slope and off the cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:21.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here's the diver's report.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:25.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hand brake of the car underwater\Nwas disengaged, just as we suspected.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.09,0:07:29.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, we found this lying on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.22,0:07:31.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a lockpick!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:33.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're dealing with a pro here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.22,0:07:35.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been wiped clean of prints!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:37.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you find any other clues?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:39.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:43.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just a puddle of water that must've\Nleaked out of the car's air conditioner
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.56,0:07:47.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,where the car was parked\Nin the parking lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.90,0:07:53.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, did you notice any\Nsuspicious figures around the car?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:54.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dunno...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:59.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't sleep much last night,\Nso I was sound asleep in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:03.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But ever since we arrived in Izu,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:07.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,someone suspicious has been\Ntailing us for some reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.59,0:08:09.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that's him over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.68,0:08:14.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pardon my rudeness,\Nbut could you identify yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.47,0:08:17.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I work at the inn where\Nthe girls are staying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.47,0:08:22.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The inn's not busy\Nduring the afternoon,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:25.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I had some free time,\Nso I came here today to have some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:28.65,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He isn't behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:35.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}When the car started moving, he was\Nalready in the restaurant with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.53,0:08:39.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If he'd forced the car door open,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.41,0:08:43.46,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}released the hand brake,\Nand then come into the restaurant,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.50,0:08:48.21,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}we would have seen him\Ncome in through the entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:54.38,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}When I asked the waiter, he told me\Nthat the back door is always kept locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.05,0:08:58.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We first noticed him when\Nhe came out of the restroom,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:02.73,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}but there's no window leading out\Nfrom inside that restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.10,0:09:06.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And of course, Michiwaki{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}'s\Nin the clear too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.77,0:09:12.32,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He was eating with us\Nand never left the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:14.36,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:18.91,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The most likely suspect is\Nthe man who's been following us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.45,0:09:20.99,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Who is he anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:28.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listen up, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:30.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll take all your statements\Ndown at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.96,0:09:32.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So please get into the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.34,0:09:34.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The car?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.84,0:09:38.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,U-Umm, I don't feel like\Nriding in a car right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.80,0:09:40.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm kinda scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.85,0:09:44.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then how about I walk you\Nto the police station?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.39,0:09:50.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not that far, and we can\Nenjoy the scenery. How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.82,0:09:52.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:55.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-Wait just a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:09:58.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What if she gets attacked again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:10:00.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} does have\Nbrown hair, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:03.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her assailant could also be\Nthe same killer from that other case.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:06.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.08,0:10:09.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No one would be foolish enough to attack her in broad daylight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:12.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,B-But you never know!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:14.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.59,0:10:16.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Michiwaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} will be with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.30,0:10:18.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if worse comes\Nto worst, so will Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.05,0:10:23.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just don't stop anywhere.\NCome straight to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:25.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.82,0:10:38.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.15,0:10:41.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The attack at the inn last night,\Nand then the car incident today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.20,0:10:42.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They sure are after you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:46.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko, are you sure you don't\Nhave any idea what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.20,0:10:47.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, none at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.41,0:10:50.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's because\Nyou're so charming?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.88,0:10:54.38,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Right, why is she being targeted?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:11:01.34,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And if he was after her life, why didn't\Nhe do it when he broke into the car?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.01,0:11:08.81,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There was no need to put the car in gear\Nand have it plunge off the cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.77,0:11:13.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we planned on going home as soon\Nas we had lunch at the restaurant,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:16.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so all of our luggage\Nwas in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.11,0:11:17.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all gone up in flames now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.32,0:11:22.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, why do we have to\Nbe put through all of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.07,0:11:23.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yours is nothing in comparison!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.78,0:11:25.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, I lost my car!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:28.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:29.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just because you got\Ninvolved with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.87,0:11:31.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess I brought you bad luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:34.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. That's not right, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:37.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's nothing compared to losing\Nall the memorable photos you took.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:39.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Photos are something\Nyou can never replace.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.92,0:11:44.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All that's left now\Nis that one photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:45.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.26,0:11:48.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, the one I'm going\Nto show Shin'ichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.56,0:11:50.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have it on me at all times—\Nyou have nothing to worry about!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.02,0:11:53.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You still have it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.10,0:11:56.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C'mon, get rid of it!\NYou're making me mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.98,0:11:58.82,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's it!\NIt's that photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.82,0:12:02.36,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm certain the killer wants\Nto get rid of that photo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.16,0:12:08.16,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's why he had to send the car\Nover the cliff to get rid of Sonoko's luggage!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.41,0:12:11.50,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But I don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.25,0:12:17.09,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why does he think Sonoko took\Nan incriminating picture of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:22.97,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There wasn't a single unusual\Nphoto in the ones she took.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:27.47,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Or did I overlook something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.82,0:12:39.07,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's him again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:41.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think we're being followed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.03,0:12:44.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it the killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.66,0:12:45.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you run?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.95,0:12:47.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.07,0:12:47.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.41,0:12:51.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.92,0:13:04.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But isn't it more dangerous\Nto go through the woods?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:06.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, this is more thrilling!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.09,0:13:07.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.76,0:13:08.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.68,0:13:11.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's split up\Nto shake him off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.11,0:13:20.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.40,0:13:24.32,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If he's Sonoko's attacker,\Nwhy's he still after her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.32,0:13:26.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}All the photos were burned!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.49,0:13:32.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A train?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.79,0:13:36.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Come to think of it, they found\Na body in this forest yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:42.00,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}When we passed this place a couple\Nnights ago, I'm sure a train went by.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.76,0:13:45.47,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.18,0:13:47.43,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm missing something here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:04.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn! I've lost them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:07.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The situation's turning bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.49,0:14:12.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Enough is enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.58,0:14:16.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you thought we'd just run,\Nyou've made a big mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.08,0:14:18.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:21.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Owowowowow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:24.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't have run\Nthrough the forest in sandals!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:26.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sandals?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.97,0:14:27.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was you, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.76,0:14:30.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the one who attacked\NSonoko last night at the inn,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:32.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and sent the car over the cliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.26,0:14:35.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hold on there! That's—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.35,0:14:37.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No use lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.81,0:14:39.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your hairy arms\Nare proof enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.69,0:14:41.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's have a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:44.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There should be bite marks\Nwhere Sonoko bit you last night!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.19,0:14:48.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No way...\NThere's no bite marks!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:50.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe on the other arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:53.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? No marks on\Nthis arm either!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:14:55.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.33,0:14:56.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who are you anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.91,0:14:57.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:15:00.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a detective with the Chiba\NPrefecture Police Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.67,0:15:03.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're just showing me the cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.34,0:15:06.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're dead wrong if you think\NI'd fall for that trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.17,0:15:09.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My father used to be a police\Nofficer. You can't fool me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.43,0:15:13.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When an officer has to\Nidentify him or herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:16.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they must show the first page\Nof the police notebook
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.14,0:15:17.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,with the photo\Nand corresponding data.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.14,0:15:21.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The name's Shoji Terabayashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.06,0:15:23.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, my.\NIt's the real thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:26.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm on the trail of a suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.57,0:15:28.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A suspect?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:30.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.07,0:15:33.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't usually wear\Nsocks with sandals, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.53,0:15:36.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:37.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:38.70,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sonoko's in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.16,0:15:40.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.67,0:15:43.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I stepped on a twig.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:46.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess running about in the forest\Nwith sandals wasn't such a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:48.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:52.93,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Tooth marks...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.39,0:16:01.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you so surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.98,0:16:06.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's nothing to be so\Nsurprised about, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.27,0:16:08.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.86,0:16:12.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the mark\Nyou gave me last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.87,0:16:21.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So {\i1}that's{\i0} it!\NThat's what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:26.13,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sonoko didn't bite his arm\Nlast night—she bit his leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:27.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She must've gotten\Nmixed up in the dark!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.30,0:16:31.63,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He probably thought\NSonoko took his picture
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.42,0:16:35.22,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}because the sparks the\Ntrain's pantograph produces
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.93,0:16:38.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}lit him from behind\Nat the time of the murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.60,0:16:42.31,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And seeing Sonoko, who passed by\Nholding a camera immediately after that,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:43.73,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}he jumped to\Nthe wrong conclusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.65,0:16:47.31,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He thought he'd\Nbeen seen with the victim!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:51.03,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Come to think of it,\NI remember him saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.40,0:16:56.07,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Don't worry. You look\Ngood in anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.07,0:16:57.91,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yukata, swimsuit, whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.58,0:17:02.25,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The only time Sonoko wore a yukata was\Nduring the fireworks show two nights ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.08,0:17:04.87,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We only met him yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:07.33,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He wouldn't have known\Nwhat she looks like in a yukata!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:10.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Damn it! Why didn't I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.17,0:17:12.76,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why didn't I figure it out sooner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.09,0:17:15.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.59,0:17:17.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give me that picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:21.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The picture you were going to\Nhave some detective look at!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.39,0:17:25.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You probably planned on taking\Na romantic picture of a couple,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.56,0:17:28.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but that photo shows me in the\Nmiddle of committing murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:30.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just like I am now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:33.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,F-Four?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.07,0:17:35.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Michiwaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} killed four people?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:38.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he was responsible for\Nthe murder the other night,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.07,0:17:39.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then she's probably the fourth!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.49,0:17:41.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For some reason, he only\Nkills girls with brown hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.45,0:17:44.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've had my eyes on\Nhim for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:47.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got him on a stolen\Nvehicle charge once,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.83,0:17:49.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but there wasn't enough\Nproof on the murder charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.96,0:17:54.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I came to Izu because I heard that\Na similar murder happened here,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.13,0:17:56.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and here he was!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.43,0:18:00.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I arrived too late\Nto save his latest victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:02.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's something\NI still don't get.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.81,0:18:06.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did he make the car move on its own\Nif he was in the restaurant the whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.31,0:18:08.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.35,0:18:11.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He had a cooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:15.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He took a wedge-shaped\Npiece of ice out,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:19.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and placed it under the left front tire\Nto prevent it from moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.91,0:18:23.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then he pretended to talk to\NSonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r} who was inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:26.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and released the hand brake!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.33,0:18:30.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then he left a\Nlockpick on the ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.42,0:18:33.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to divert the investigation!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.96,0:18:35.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:39.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why he left two\Nspaces open when he parked!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:42.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then there'd be no cars obstructing\Nhis car's path when it moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:48.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On top of that, the melted ice would\Njust appear to be water from the AC.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.27,0:18:50.65,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:52.94,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why does he kill only\Ngirls with brown hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.48,0:18:56.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you, didn't I?\NA heartless girl dumped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.07,0:18:59.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that's... That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.45,0:19:02.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whenever I see flirty girls like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.16,0:19:04.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get so mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.45,0:19:09.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Especially when I see girls with brown hair,\Njust like the one who dumped me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.33,0:19:12.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look over there!\NIsn't that Sonoko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.08,0:19:12.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.54,0:19:14.96,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:18.76,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why? Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.26,0:19:22.05,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why are all the guys that\Nmake a play for me so weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.05,0:19:25.31,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I hate you, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.11,0:19:34.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:36.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-Am {\i1}I{\i0} all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:37.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about {\i1}you{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.90,0:19:39.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.91,0:19:49.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:53.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew I'd seen that guy\Nwith the glasses before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.17,0:19:54.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was at the tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:59.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the captain of the Haido\NHigh School Karate Club!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.80,0:20:01.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Prince of Kicks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.39,0:20:06.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Makoto Kyogoku!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.68,0:20:10.14,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:13.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're a very reckless lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.44,0:20:18.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're lucky I was nearby\Nand had some free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:20.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,F-Free time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.15,0:20:22.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you mean you were\Nfollowing me all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.90,0:20:26.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I was following you\Nthe whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:27.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until I lost sight\Nof you in the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.45,0:20:32.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew you might mistake\Nme for a stalker.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.62,0:20:36.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before he met you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.08,0:20:40.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he'd been flirting\Nwith a few other girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.13,0:20:41.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It got me worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.26,0:20:45.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you worry about me?\NYou don't even know me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.09,0:20:48.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You probably didn't notice me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.05,0:20:52.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I'd seen you once before,\Nat a karate tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.43,0:20:55.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were cheering on your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.31,0:20:59.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never thought you'd\Nreserve a room in our inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.03,0:21:04.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.07,0:21:09.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd like to recommend that,\Nas much possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.08,0:21:12.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you avoid wearing those lingerie-like outfits that arouse men.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.00,0:21:16.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, you're free\Nto ignore my advice,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.12,0:21:19.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and pass it off as\Njust another casual remark
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.50,0:21:22.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,made by one of\Nyour many admirers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.03,0:23:10.61,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Teitan High School
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.11,0:23:10.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kyogoku{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s gone abroad to study?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.24,0:23:12.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.62,0:23:15.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You and he were getting along\Nso well since then, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.62,0:23:20.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said he ran out of strong opponents\Nin Japan, so he went abroad to train.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.12,0:23:27.30,Signs,,0,0,0,,THREE DAYS LATER
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.75,0:23:23.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.92,0:23:27.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go see the baseball team's practice game!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.67,0:23:30.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The other team's ace is a\Nfirst-year high school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.18,0:23:33.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hear he's so cute\Nand just so adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.64,0:23:34.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.60,0:23:36.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought you were going to wait\Nfor Kyogoku{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.43,0:23:40.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's that, this is this!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.23,0:23:43.77,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.49,0:23:56.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A key in the water?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.12,0:23:57.74,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The window?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.83,0:24:00.04,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.04,0:24:03.46,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's no way a person\Ncould come in through that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.50,0:24:08.96,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Just what trick was used to\Nturn this into a locked room?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.96,0:24:15.01,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.26,0:24:20.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Crayons
